    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1189">
<l>pacakkamaṟ paṭṭāṅkeṉ mēṉi nayappittār </l>
<l> namnilaiya rāva reṉiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If he is clear of guilt who has conciliated me (to his departure) let my body suffer its due and turn sallow.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
